<br>
I always keep a pet up, however, and I have yet to ask for anyone to buff it in any way.  I will haste it though, and 99% of the time my pet is not taking any damage.  The pet costs me a tiny dagger and a bit of mana - cheap cheap cheap.  So it dies?  Big deal, cast another.  Not many classes can cast pets as cheap (or as stupid) as these.<br>
