<br>
If you've got a group comprised of mainly raid guilders with large numbers of AA's who're slumming it in Normal, then what you need is six damage dealers.  In an undead-heavy dungeon where I have no healing or pulling responsibilities, I can kick out about 70 DPS - and Blackwinter is going to exceed that HUGELY.<br>
<br>
On the other hand, if you've got a group comprised of mainly raid guilders in Normal, then even six clerics are probably going to succeed.<br>
<br>
